title: Broncos-Jets TNF Recap: How much longer do Adam Gase and Sam Darnold have left in New York? (Football 10/2)
description:
The Broncos beat the Jets 37-28 on Thursday Night Football, so guess who we're talking about? Of course it's the losing side, as we focus Sam Darnold and Adam Gase! The Jets are embarrassing but that doesn't necessarily mean a change is coming at head coach. Could a change be coming at quarterback if they get the #1 pick though? Don't worry, Denver does get some credit. Brett Rypien had some bad moments but was serviceable in his first NFL start. The Pick Six Superfriends share all their takeaways on this lengthy TNF Recap episode.
